  <brief_title>Study of Anti-atherosclerotic Activity of Inflaminat in Asymptomatic Participants With Subclinical Atherosclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double-blinded Placebo-controlled Multicenter Study of Anti-atherosclerotic Activity of Inflaminat in Asymptomatic Participants With Subclinical Atherosclerosis</official_title>
