  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the anti-atherosclerotic effect of long-term
      anti-inflammatory therapy (Inflaminat) in asymptomatic participants with subclinical
      atherosclerosis of carotid arteries.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
